cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2C to the same IP as GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF will cause IP address conflict and prevent X2-C interface establishment.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2C 設定為與 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 相同的 IP 會導致 IP 地址衝突，並阻止 X2-C 接口建立。

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA to the same value as absoluteFrequencySSB will cause frequency misalignment and prevent proper carrier configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA 設定為與 absoluteFrequencySSB 相同的值會導致頻率錯位，並阻止正確的載波配置。
